                    "kind": "text",
                    "text": "Lazily derive the key once; cache the (non-extractable) CryptoKey\nin memory only. Concurrent calls share one in-flight derivation. A\nrejected derivation is NOT cached — the next call retries."
                  }
                ]
              },
